comments: Temple (CHI) reaches across Beal's (WAS) body and initiates contact that affects his FOM.
White (CHI) sets the screen on Bertans (WAS) gives him room to avoid the contact.
Len (WAS) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Temple (CHI) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Len (WAS) makes marginal contact with Young (CHI) at the end of his drive.
Beal (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position on LaVine (CHI) during the drive.
Williams (CHI) makes contact with Len's (WAS) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Young (CHI) sets the screen on Beal (WAS) and does not deliver contact.
Len (WAS) makes contact with LaVine's (CHI) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Len (WAS) sets the screen on Temple (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Young (CHI) makes contact with Beal's (WAS) arm and affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Hachimura (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position on LaVine (CHI) during the drive.
Hachimura (WAS) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Smith (WAS) and Williams (CHI) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Temple (CHI) sets the screen on Len (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Len (WAS) sets the screen on Temple (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Temple (CHI) reaches in and makes contact with Beal's (WAS) arm that affects his shot attempt.

Len (WAS) jumps and maintains a vertical position to absorb the contact from LaVine (CHI) during the shot attempt. After the initial contact Len brings his arm down and does not make contact with LaVine.
Valentine (CHI) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
